  "texts": [
    "The models were loaded on a pair of Nvidia A6000s with NVlink and a total Video Random Access Memory (VRAM) capacity of 96 GB.",
    "The 65B model was run in 8-bit mode to fit in the available VRAM.",
    "We used the llamaprecise parameter preset and fixed zero seed for reproducibility.",
    "Llama 2 was evaluated using the demo on huggingface.",
    "To rigorously assess the models, we prepared 20 questions of varying complexity based on two types of context material: half from operating manuals and half from unstructured issue reports."
  ],
